 normal; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://academy.fengniao.com/534/pic_5349201_21.html\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><img src=\"https://cms.qn.img-space.com/product/158/164/ceuo0I7pmNuXs.jpg?imageView2/2/w/700/h/2000/q/90/ignore-error/1/\" width=\"700\" height=\"408\" title=\"让你的边缘锐化不再有白边 边缘蒙版\" alt=\"让你的边缘锐化不再有白边 边缘蒙版\" align=\"no\" style=\"border: 1px solid black; vertical-align: top;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://academy.fengniao.com/534/pic_5349201_22.html\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><img src=\"https://cms.qn.img-space.com/product/158/165/ceOC1b7LMv4Mo.jpg?imageView2/2/w/700/h/2000/q/90/ignore-error/1/\" width=\"700\" height=\"396\" title=\"让你的边缘锐化不再有白边 边缘蒙版\" alt=\"让你的边缘锐化不再有白边 边缘蒙版\" align=\"no\" style=\"border: 1px solid black; vertical-align: top;\"/></a><br/><strong>还是按照之前锐化的参数，因为边缘蒙版，白边儿被隐藏，白边儿消失</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal;\">　　有了边缘蒙版之后，白边儿被隐藏；边缘蒙版可以很好的解决锐化带来的白边儿问题。</p><p><br/></p>','2018-02-26 21:06:12','/upload/gallery/8/7eca5fd568be90d03597f5b78fe3f87c.jpg,/upload/gallery/8/26621b443fdd99f2f416335cdf1c90d2.jpg,/upload/gallery/8/2094619008b1061561b6644c57305a9a.jpg,','摄影,蒙版','让你的边缘锐化不再有白边 边缘蒙版',10,1,2,'在摄影后期中：锐化的时候，经常会出现一些难看、尴尬的白边儿，非常的影响效果，相信每个人都有这样的经历。这个是和锐化的原理有关——锐化就是在细节边缘建立黑边儿、白边儿，增加局部对比度，来提升锐度。　　只要是锐化，必然会产生白边儿，不可避免，但是我们可以用边缘蒙版，让白边不显现出来；从此不再有这种尴尬的白边儿存在！　　边缘蒙版也可以建立成一个动作，需要时直接调取即可。两张照片上，都有不同程度的白边先模',3,'/upload/gallery/8/2094619008b1061561b6644c57305a9a.jpg',NULL,4,0),(103,1,0,'<p>摘要：Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，今天蚂蚁摄影教你如何拍出更漂亮的光斑。我们会用最通俗易懂的语言让您利用短短5分钟的学习就能拍出好照片。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用通俗易懂的语言5分钟教您拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教你如何拍出更漂亮的光斑。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，<a href=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;\">摄影艺术吧</a>文字整理，如需转载请保留来源。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S4125L5-0.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">上篇教程蚂蚁给大家讲了怎么拍出梦幻光斑，大家应该都学会了吧，简单回忆下当时的要点：</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">①建议最好在晚上灯火辉煌的街道拍摄或装有灯饰的室内拍摄；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">②调到AV档，设置最大光圈，设置ISO为自动；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">③将自动对焦AF调成手动对焦MF；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">④对着霓虹灯等光源转动对焦环到最模糊后按快门拍掇。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">今天蚂蚁更进一步，教大家怎么把光斑拍的更漂亮。首当其冲就是如下图这样的心形光斑，当然除了教大家怎么拍心形光斑之外，蚂蚁还会教大家几个小技巧，可以把光斑拍的更美更有味道，赶紧往下看↓↓↓</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">温馨提示：因为拍光斑很多基础的知识点蚂蚁在上篇教程都讲过了，这篇就不再重复了，没有看过上篇光斑教程的小伙伴建议大家看看，否则这篇教程看起来可能会很吃力（看上篇光斑教程点击一下“光斑”即可进去教程）。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S22A0J-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">器材要求：和上篇教程一样，拍光斑需要支持MF手动对焦的相机，一般单反都支持，如果你的相机不是单反，记得查一下是否支持MF手动对焦。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">示范机型：佳能700D+18-55mm镜头+50/1.8佳能定焦头。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">蚂蚁首先给大家总结下拍摄更美丽光斑的要领：</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">①用MF手动对焦拍一些心形等不同形状且画面只有光斑的照片：首先，准备一张黑色的纸片，然后按照镜头的外圈直径在黑纸上画个圆，最后用剪刀剪下来。其次，需要在这张圆纸片的中间剪出一个心形的形状。最后，把心形剪下来并扣在镜头的前面，然后你只需按照光斑教程（上）讲的步骤，就能拍出心形光斑了。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">②用AF自动对焦并利用背景虚化来拍光斑，而且可以配上一些文字，还可以试试在利用玻璃上的水滴来拍摄光斑等。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">好了，赶紧开始蚂蚁的详细教程吧↓↓↓</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">以下所有文字均为蚂蚁原创，图片蚂蚁均有版权，转载请注明出处。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">第一用 MF手动对焦拍心形等不同形状且画面只有光斑的照片，需在黑纸上剪出心形的形状，并覆盖在镜头上拍摄</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">怎么拍出下图1.1这样的心形光斑呢？需要借助一个小道具，然后再按照光斑教程（上）讲到的方法拍摄就可以了。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S22B447-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">图1.1 新型光斑</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">01 首先，准备一张黑色的纸片，然后按照镜头的外圈直径在黑纸上画个圆，最后用剪刀剪下来（见下图1.2)。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2261S5-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">图1.2 照镜头画个圆并用剪刀剪下来</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">02 其次，需要在这张圆纸片的中间剪个心形的形状，那么问题是：我们需要剪一个多大的心形呢？这个心形的大小是有讲究的，笼统的说，你所画心形的大小要小于镜头当前焦段下最大光圈直径的大小，见右图1.3的示意图。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S22A5B-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">图1.3 心形直径要小于当前焦段镜头最大光圈的直径</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">看到这里大家可能有点模糊了，最大光圈直径如何得知呢？没关系，其实特别简单，给大家举两个例子大家就知道了。比如你用18-55的镜头，在18mm焦段拍摄，此焦段下镜头的最大光圈为F3.5，那么最大光圈的直径是：18/3.5=5.1mm，再比如，你在55mm焦段拍摄，在这个焦段镜头的最大光圈是F5.6，那么最大光圈的直径是：55/5.6=9.8mm。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">也就是说，如果你在18mm焦段拍心形光斑，你在黑纸片上剪出的心形直径要小于5.1mm，如果你在55mm焦段拍摄，你剪出的心形直径要小于9.8mm。这下你明白了吗？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">其实道理很简单，如果你的心形比光圈都大，就相当于心形里面包含光圈，光线还是从原来的光圈进入，心形的作用就失效了，和没挡纸片一样，自然拍不出心形的光斑了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">03 最后，把心形剪下来并扣在镜头的前面（见下图1.4)，然后你只需按照光斑教程（上）讲的步骤，就能拍出上图1.1那样的心形光斑了。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2262934-5.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">图1.4 把心形剪下来并扣在镜头的前面</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">看到这里想必你已经完全懂了，如果我按照上面的要求，在黑纸片上剪出如下图1.5那样的五角星形状，自然就可以拍出如下图1.6那样五角星形状的光斑。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2264463-6.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图1.5 在黑制片上剪出五角星的形状</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2263205-7.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图1.6 五角星形的光斑</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">第二 用AF自动对焦，在AV档下设置最大光圈、设置自动ISO，利用背景虚化来拍光斑</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">我们前面讲的都是利用MF手动对焦或借助小道具拍光斑的方法，其实还有一种最简单的办法，就是在AF自动对焦模式下，调到AV光圈优先模式，设置最大光圈，设置自动ISO，利用背景虚化的方法拍光斑，比如下图2.1这样的照片，把灯笼当成主体，把灯笼后的灯光虚化成光斑。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2261293-8.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">图2.1 主体是灯笼｜背景是光斑</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">这样的照片说白了就是拍背景虚化，背景虚化的方法还记得吗？开启大变焦，开启大光圈，尽量靠近被摄物体，让被摄物体离背景远一些，然后在AF下对焦到灯笼上，光斑就形成了（如果想详细了解背景虚化的拍摄方法的，请点击“背景虚化”即可）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">如果你想拍像下图2.2那样人物后面有光斑的照片，方法和拍灯笼是一样的，同样是利用大光圈等背景虚化的方法拍(如果你想详细了解如何拍人物后面有光斑的照片，可以点击査看专题文章夜景人像下集教程）。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S22CS0-9.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">图2.2 背景是光斑的夜景人像</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#3366ff;box-sizing: border-box;\">小知识：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#3366ff;box-sizing: border-box;\">①我们还可以在图片上写上几行字，能更加突出某种氛围，马上就让照片感觉有了故事，可谓是点睛之笔了。至于如何添加文字，现在一些像美图秀秀、光影魔术手等简单的后期软件都可以添加文字。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#3366ff;box-sizing: border-box;\">②当然，我们也可以学习剪心形光斑的方法，将心形的黑纸扣在镜头上，然后利用背景虚化的方法拍出主体清晰，而背景是其他形状光斑的照片(见图2.3）。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2263D0-10.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">图2.3 利用背景虚化拍的心形光斑</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#3366ff;box-sizing: border-box;\">③可以利用玻璃上的水滴来拍光斑</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">在下雨天，车窗或者家里的玻璃上会布满水珠，这时你可以透过玻璃拍光斑，在布满水珠的玻璃外面是漂亮的光斑，整个气氛犹如一个正在哭泣的美少女，如梦如痴（见下图2.4)。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2262063-11.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">图2.4 在雨天拍摄的光斑</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">拍这样的照片，其实和上面提到的通过灯笼虚化光斑一样，是在AF自动对焦状态下，对焦在水滴上，将水滴拍清楚，把光斑虚化。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">好了，上面蚂蚊讲了几种拍美丽光斑的方法，最后我们回顾总结下：</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">①用MF手动对焦拍一些心形等不同形状且画面只有光斑的照片：首先，准备一张黑色的纸片，然后按照镜头的外圈直径在黑纸上画个圆，最后用剪刀剪下来。其次，需要在这张圆纸片的中间剪出一个心形的形状。最后，把心形剪下来并扣在镜头的前面，然后你只需按照光斑教程（上）讲的步骤，就能拍出心形光斑了。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">②用AF自动对焦并利用背景虚化来拍光斑，而且可以配上一些文字，还可以试试在利用玻璃上的水滴来拍摄光斑等。</span></p><p><br/></p>','2018-02-27 17:05:56','http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S4125L5-0.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S22A0J-1.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S22B447-2.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2261S5-3.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S22A5B-4.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2262934-5.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2264463-6.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2263205-7.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2261293-8.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S22CS0-9.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2263D0-10.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2262063-11.jpg','摄影,光斑','教你如何拍出更漂亮的光斑',6,0,0,'摘要：Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，今天蚂蚁摄影教你如何拍出更漂亮的光斑。我们会用最通俗易懂的语言让您利用短短5分钟的学习就能拍出好照片。Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用通俗易懂的语言5分钟教您拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教你如何拍出更漂亮的光斑。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，摄影艺术吧文字整理，如需转载请保留来源。上篇教程蚂蚁给大家讲了怎么拍出',1,'http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1S2262063-11.jpg',NULL,4,0),(104,1,0,'<p style=\"text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用通俗易懂的语言5分钟教您拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教你如何手持拍夜景。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，<a href=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;\">摄影艺术吧</a>文字整理，如需转载请保留来源。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J15314S-0.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">内容简介：如何手持拍夜景 示范机型：佳能700D</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">蚂蚁曾经出过一篇如何拍夜景的教程，里面讲到为了避免模糊要使用三脚架保持相机的稳定（没看过之前夜景教程的同学可以点击“夜景”查看），但很多时候我们看到漂亮的夜景想拍下来，手边却恰好没带三脚架应该怎么办呢？蚂蚁今天就教大家在没有三脚架的情况下怎么手持拍夜景，和利用三脚架拍夜景的步骤方法完全不同哦，大家仔细看。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J1531200-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">烟台山公园蚂蚁用佳能700D手持拍摄</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在很多相机都有手持夜景模式，如果你的相机有这个模式，用这个模式拍出来的夜景也还不错，如果没有，那就按照下边的步骤来吧，照样能拍的很出色：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">1关闭闪光灯；2把相机调到TV档，设置最低1/30S的快门速度；3设置ISO为自动；4保持正确的拍照姿势，尽量找固定支撑物帮助稳定相机。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面赶紧进入我们的详细教程↓↓↓</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">1、关闭闪光灯</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">和前一篇夜景教程一样，一定要关闭闪光灯。因为相机的闪光灯一般只有3-5米的照射范围，所以只能照亮你身前3-5米的景物，而后面的景色因为照射不到就更加黑暗。看下图1.1和图1.2的对比。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J153L96-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图1.1前景的汽车亮和树过量后景色建筑过暗</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J1536293-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图1.2前后景亮暗合适</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">2、调到TV档，设置最慢1/30秒或者更快的快门</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">把相机顶部的模式转盘转到TV档（即快门优先模式，见下图2.1），设置最慢1/30S的快门速度（想详细了解快门知识的同学请点击“快门”即可）。经过蚂蚁反复测试，如果快门速度比这个值还慢，那手持拍出来的基本都是模糊的，你不要告诉我你是铁手，可以手持相机纹丝不动，如果你确实具备此超能力，同学，请直接关闭本教程，地球已经不适合你生存了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你的相机没有TV模式，可以调到P模式，跳过此步直接看第三步，但是因为无法设置快门，很可能拍出来是模糊的，这个软是相机的硬伤了，木办法啊。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J1531025-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图2.1转动转盘到TV模式</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J1534608-5.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图2.2TV模式下快门设置为1/30S</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#3366ff;box-sizing: border-box;\">小知识/Tidbits</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#3366ff;box-sizing: border-box;\">上面提到的1/30S的快门速度是在不开启变焦的情况下而言的，如果你拍长焦，你会发现即便设置1/30S的快门拍出来也模糊？怎么回事？蚂蚁的经验不对？</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#3366ff;box-sizing: border-box;\">非也非也，告诉个计算方法，假设你用佳能700D+18-55mm镜头并在55焦段拍摄，那么你设置的快门应不能低于1/55S，没错，是焦距的倒数，你太聪明了同学。记住了，开启的变焦越大，相应的就要把快门速度设置的越快才能保证手持拍摄清晰。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">3、把ISO设置成自动</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">经常看蚂蚁教程的同学都知道，ISO太高了会导致画面粗糙，影响画质（想详细了解ISO知识的同学，请点击“ISO”即进入教程），所以蚂蚁一般建议大家ISO最高也不要超过400。但是今时不同往日了啊同学，晚上光线那么暗，你还设置了1/30S的快门，即便TV模式下相机会自动匹配一个较大的光圈，画面也可能会非常暗，所以此时就不得不提高ISO来增加画面的亮度了，说白了就是牺牲画质换取照片的正常亮度。（看不太懂？叫你不看蚂蚁的教程，该补补课了，请点击“曝光”，看完你就懂了）。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J153L96-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">图3把ISO设置为AUTO自动</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那么为什么ISO设置为自动呢？（见上图3）因为各位所拍摄的夜景光线情况千差万别，蚂蚁也不好给出一个定值，所以设置成自动，相机会根据你的光线情况自动给出合适的ISO值。如果光线还比较足，相机可能给一个200的ISO就欧了，如果光线很差，相机可能会给出一个3200的ISO，懂了吧？</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">4、保持正确的拍照姿势</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一定要保证正确的拍照姿势，这样能最大程度的保持相机稳定，否则很可能1/30S的快门你拍出来的都是模糊的。像下图4.1中的模特学习：右手握住相机并负责按快门，左手托住镜头，双臂在身体两侧自然夹紧（想了解更多正确的拍照姿势，请点击“拍照姿势”即可）。如果此时身边有固定物体比如大树、栏杆等，应果断猛靠上去，为了拍出清晰的夜景大片，拼了吧。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J1534C3-7.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图4.1保持正确的拍照姿势</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J15324L-8.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图4.2借助固定物体保持稳定</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#3366ff;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">小窍门/Tips</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#3366ff;box-sizing: border-box;\">蚂蚁手持拍夜景最喜欢找垃圾桶电线杆子等帮助支撑身体，这样蚂蚁就可以把快门设置成1/20S或者更慢，拍得照样很清楚，ISO就可以不用那么高，画质就会好一点，你学会了吗？</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">完成以上四步之后，手持拍摄夜景也能得到很不错的效果了，下面看一下蚂蚁团队手持拍摄的夜景照片。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">看完上面的介绍，最后总结一下拍夜景的设置方法：</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">1/关闭闪光灯；</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">2/把相机调到TV档，设置最低1/30S的快门速度；</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">3/设置ISO为自动；</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">4/保持正确的拍照姿势，尽量找固定支撑物帮助稳定相机。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p>','2018-02-27 17:09:08','http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J15314S-0.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J1531200-1.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J153L96-2.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J1536293-3.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J1531025-4.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J1534608-5.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J153L96-2.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J1534C3-7.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J15324L-8.jpg','摄影,夜景','教你如何手持拍夜景',3,0,0,'Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用通俗易懂的语言5分钟教您拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教你如何手持拍夜景。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，摄影艺术吧文字整理，如需转载请保留来源。内容简介：如何手持拍夜景 示范机型：佳能700D蚂蚁曾经出过一篇如何拍夜景的教程，里面讲到为了避免模糊要使用三脚架保持相机的稳定（没看过之前夜景教程的同学可以点击“夜景”查看），',1,'http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1J15324L-8.jpg',NULL,4,0),(105,1,0,'<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用通俗易懂的语言5分钟教您拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教你如何用手机拍好美食。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，<a href=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;\">摄影艺术吧</a>文字整理，如需转载请保留来源。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G435FM-0.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">每天凌晨12点左右，蚂蚁的QQ群里就开始热闹起来，了解的人都知道BOSS又在给晚上值班的小伙伴们“发福利了”，各种诱人的美食照片开始涌现，试想一下，在午夜12点，本已饥肠辘辘的客服们一边服务顾客，一边满眼全是看到却吃不到的美食，那是一种什么样的感受？简直要抓狂啊有木有？在这里蚂蚁必须对BOSS这种惨无人道的行为进行深深的谴责，唉，于心何忍啊。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">美食我想不仅仅是蚂蚁BOSS的爱好，现在谁出去吃饭还不拍个照片刷个朋友圈呢？这已然成为一种在移动互联网大潮下形成的生活方式，那今天蚂蚁就教教大家怎么拍美食。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3496311-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#008080;box-sizing: border-box;\">小白拍照还是那两个需求：第一/拍的出来，第二/拍的好看。</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于美食来说，人人都能拍的出来，所以拍的好看才是大家的诉求，蚂蚁本篇文章主要从构图和拍摄角度等方面教大家怎么把美食拍的好看。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">器材要求：模拟大家拍美食的主要场景，20%的情况下出去旅游，吃货们会用相机记录美食，80%的情况是下各种馆子，手机是主要的拍摄器材，所以我们这篇教程的主要拍摄工具就是手机，当然如果你是相机的话也没所谓，因为讲构图和角度，手机和相机都是一样的。只不过相机的色彩和虚化能力确实比手机要强悍一些，特别是在弱光环境下相机的优势更明显一些。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">另外，既然是讲手机拍照，蚂蚁后面还会有一小部分内容教大家怎么用手机上的APP，把美食照片优化的更好看，瞬间让你的逼格满满的，春节时可以好好显摆显摆了，哈哈。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">光线要求：如果白天室外，光线自然不是问题，白天室内的话最好找靠窗的位置，利用自然光拍摄，如果靠窗的位罝不好找或者晚上光线不足的情况，可能就要补光哦，这个蚂蚁有妙招，接着往下看。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【以下所有文字均为蚂蚁原创，图片蚂蚁均有版权，转载请注明出处】</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">第一，多尝试不同的拍摄角度</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们先从拍摄角度上来说，美食的拍摄角度大致有三种：从美食正上方俯拍、侧面平视拍摄和斜上方拍摄。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">01从美食正上方俯拍</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G34aG9-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">正上方拍得披萨和南瓜汤/图1.1</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你想要拍摄美食的全貌或风声的场面，可以试试从顶部垂直往下拍摄，并注意尽量找一些其他物件点缀一下，见左图1.1，蚂蚁从正上方拍摄PIZZA，把PIZZA摆在画面左下角，右上角放一碗南瓜粥点缀，会让画面显得更有格调，避免呆板。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">采用这个角度时如果灯光在你头顶或者你的身后，那问题来了，你的手、手机或者身体会遮挡光线导致美食上有讨厌的阴影。此时你可以让你的小伙伴用他的手机闪光灯给你补光，这样在拍的时候可以减少阴影，这种补光法有个高大上的名字，叫“蚂蚁补光法”（见上图1.1蚂蚁小伙伴在右侧用手机闪光灯补光，可还是稍微有些阴影）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">[小知识]：如果你在用另外一只手机补光时发现光线不柔和，显得局部太亮太生硬，可以用餐厅的餐巾纸档在手机闪光灯的前面以达到柔化光线的作用，餐巾纸不能浪费呀，除了擦嘴用途大大滴。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">02侧而平视角度拍摄</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">星巴克或者蛋糕店的的甜品、蛋糕、冰激凌等这种有垂直高度的食物，而且侧面又比较好看的，可以试试用平视的角度拍摄（见右图1.2），这样拍摄的时候一方面要注意背景选择不要太杂乱，另外不要把食物摆在画面的正中间，可以偏左或者偏右，也可以加点缀，会更好看一些，同时在侧面平视拍摄，不会被该死的影子干扰到。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3495194-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">侧面平视拍得KFC圣代冰激凌/图1.2</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">03从美食的斜上方拍摄</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从食物的斜上方拍摄，这个拍摄角度是平时用的最多的拍摄角度，也更符合我们的拍摄习惯，这个角度既可以拍到美食的全貌，也能够最大程度的避免将阴影拍进画面，不过正是因为大家都习惯了这样拍，所以很难拍的很出彩，很难给人一种眼前一亮的“哇塞”感，这就需要在构图上下功夫，所以下面蚂蚁就给大家讲几种常用的构图方法。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3491602-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">斜上方拍得美食中规中矩/图1.3</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第二，拍美食常用的几种构图方法</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">拍摄角度你字会了，只是掌握了最基本的拍摄技巧，拍美食最出彩的地方在于构图，构图才是决定你的照片否能够逼格满满，瞬间高大上的关键。拍美食，蚂蚁建议用手机中的正方形构图，比普通的长方形构图更美。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">01用你手中的刀义、筷子、勺子等点缀美食</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们吃饭肯定离不开筷子、勺子、刀叉等，拍美食要善于利用你手中的这些家伙事儿，就比如左图2.1，你可以把筷子放在盘子、碟子的边缘作为点缀再拍摄，比单独拍一盘菜逼格瞬间提升2个档。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3492T7-5.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">用筷子点缀美食/图2.1</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">02故意不要拍全，只留出局部</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这个道理很简单，维纳斯之所以美在于他的断臂让人产生了想象的空间，蚂蚁认为如果维纳斯不是断臂的话，就不会这么出名了。美食也一样啊，犹抱琵琶半遮面，给人想象的空间呗，你以后再拍的时候，刻意只拍美食的局部，你的照片就不会那么死板了（见右图2.2）而且加上了一个汤勺作为点缀，画面立马就活了。如果你拍全了也无妨，可以通过手机中自带的编辑工具进行裁切也很方便，总之我们就是要这种残缺的效果。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3493147-6.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">可以只保留美食的局部/图2.2</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">03背景要尽量简洁</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">简洁的背景能让人把所有的目光都集中到你拍摄的美食上，避免其他视觉干扰（见下图2.3）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">04对称构图也挺好看</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有时候你可以用对称的办法来让普普通通的蛋挞也变的有点不一样（见下图2.4）。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3496220-7.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>简洁的背景/图2.3</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3494B5-8.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>对称构图拍得蛋挞图/2.4</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">05斜线构图是另一种感觉</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于一些使用长条形的餐盘盛放的食物，你还可以尝试斜线构图，照样逼格满满滴。（见右图2.5）</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3493637-9.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">斜线构图拍的鱿鱼圈/图2.5</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第三，通过靠近拍微距来表现美食的细节</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">拍美食还有一招非常实用，就是努力靠近拍摄细节。当靠的很近拍细节的时候，拍摄角度、构图方法等都已经基本用不到了，下面给大家说集中拍微距特写的实用小技巧。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">01直接靠近拍</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最简单粗暴的方法当然是直接使劲靠近拍，像拍左面的酸菜鱼，这个时候可以用小伙伴的手机闪光灯补一下光，能够让鱼表面光泽更好看更诱人，同时注意点缀，放一颗香菜在鱼上，会显得更好看（见左图3.1）。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G34a025-10.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">直接靠近拍得酸菜鱼/图3.1</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">02用筷子，汤勺等其他元素来丰富画面</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你觉得直接靠近拍太没创意啦，可以加入其他的元素，比如拍下面的米线，直接靠近拍太普通，可以用筷子夹起来再靠近拍（见右图3.2），如果是汤类的，你也可以用勺子舀一勺再拍，这个前面有讲到过吧，要活字活用。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3495194-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">用筷子加起来拍的米线/图3.2</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">03可以巧妙的利用盘子、笼屉等帮助你构建画面</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你想要拍像右图蒸饺之类的特写，你可以借助一下笼屉进行巧妙的构图（见右图3.3），是不是瞬间高大上了，比你直接靠近拍个单独的大蒸饺好看多了吧。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G34962M-12.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">用笼屉巧妙的构图/图3.3</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">04你还可以先咬一口再拍</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们要学会创新，拍出花样儿，比如左面的这个红豆饼，如果你单独拍，好像没啥可拍的，但是蚂蚁拿起来咬了一口，让里面的红豆都显露出来，再靠近了拍（见左图3.4），是不是立马不一样了？</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3494237-13.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">咬一口后拍得红豆饼/图3.4</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">05吃披萨这种粘连性的食物还可以这样拍</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你想拍披萨（高大上的英文好像是PIZZA），服务员刚刚送上的时候看起来很普通，但是蚂蚁在芝士拉丝的瞬间靠近来一张特写，效果没的说啊（见右图3.5）。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G34932N-14.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">铲起来后拍得披萨/图3.5</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第四，一些后期小技巧</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在大家的手机中都有那么几款图片类的APP，通过这些APP做一写简单的后期处理，外加使用一些滤镜，让你的美食照片变的更美。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你是iPhone，在苹果自带的相机中有铬黄滤镜，这种滤镜能让照片的色调整体偏大家可以尝试一下，蚂蚁觉得很不错。如果你是其他手机，也有很多类似的APP比如Snapseed、instagram等等，不过蚂蚁考虑装机量最高的还是美图秀秀吧，下面蚂蚁给大家介绍几个用美图秀秀后期照片的小技巧。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">01首先你拍完之后可以用美图秀秀对照片进行裁剪，一定程度上裁切照片的过程就是重新构图的过程（见下图4.1），其次，如果你感觉照片不是很清楚，你可以用锐化工具，但是要掌握度，锐化不能太过分（见下图4.2）。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3495915-15.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图片裁剪/图4.1</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G349E16-16.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图片锐化/图4.2</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">02如果你觉得亮度不够，还可以增加一些亮度；颜色不鲜艳的话就加一些饱和度；明暗对比不明显的话就加一些对比度（见右图4.3）。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3493932-17.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">饱和度、亮度、对比度/图4.3</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">03在美图秀秀里面有各种滤镜，你可以根据自己的喜好来选择，比如暖色调可以让美食更有食欲，那你就可以选择一些像秋色等暖色调的滤镜。见下图4.4蚂蚁选择的是移轴滤镜，就是相机中微缩景观的效果。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">04手机拍摄的背景虚化能力不如相机，但是没关系，我们有强大的美图秀秀，见下图4.5，你可以用背景虚化功能，把你不太想要的东西给虚掉。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3494129-18.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图片特效/图4.4</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G34942Q-19.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>背景虚化/图4.5</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">好了，看完上面的介绍是不是觉得今后你拍的美食都会逼格满满呢？话说妈蚁为了撰写此教程，一晚上换了三个地方、点了三桌菜花了500多块钱，各位看官该看的也看了，能字的也字会了，谁能把俺们这500块钱给报了？</p><p><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3495160-20.jpg\"/></p>','2018-02-27 17:11:05','http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G435FM-0.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3496311-1.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G34aG9-2.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3495194-3.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3491602-4.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3492T7-5.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3493147-6.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3496220-7.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3494B5-8.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3493637-9.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G34a025-10.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3495194-3.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G34962M-12.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3494237-13.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G34932N-14.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3495915-15.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G349E16-16.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3493932-17.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3494129-18.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G34942Q-19.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3495160-20.jpg','摄影,美食','教你如何用手机拍好美食',4,0,0,'Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用通俗易懂的语言5分钟教您拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教你如何用手机拍好美食。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，摄影艺术吧文字整理，如需转载请保留来源。每天凌晨12点左右，蚂蚁的QQ群里就开始热闹起来，了解的人都知道BOSS又在给晚上值班的小伙伴们“发福利了”，各种诱人的美食照片开始涌现，试想一下，在午夜12点，本已饥肠辘辘',1,'http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1G3495160-20.jpg',NULL,4,0),(106,1,0,'<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用通俗易懂的语言5分钟教您拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教你如何拍摄旅游摄影中的庙宇建筑-玉皇庙。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，<a href=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;\">摄影艺术吧</a>文字整理，如需转载请保留来源。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RI649-0.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　春节期间，亲朋好友吃吃喝喝之后，难免会一起到比较有名的景点逛一逛，拍拍照，但很多小伙伴往往不知道该把相机对着哪里拍，也不清楚如何选景，拍什么不拍什么。旅行回来，看看一大堆照片，场景几乎都差不多，满满的画面，大小差不多的建筑，没有特色，也没有记录下让人印象特别深刻的景物。今天蚂蚁就给大家讲一下在旅游中如何运用不同的景别来记录下多彩的旅行历程。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　景别，简单讲就是指被摄主体在画面中的范围大小。按照在画面中的范围大小主要分为全景、中景、近景和特写。景别的不同由两个因素决定：一是你与被摄体的不同距离和角度；二是拍摄时所使用的不同焦鉅。那我们该如何用不同的景别来拍摄呢？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　蚂蚁在上周末一个晴朗的下午，来到烟台的毓璜顶公园，尝试多景别拍摄公园里的玉皇庙。这次拍摄，上述两个方面的因素都涉及到了。蚂蚁不断地调整与庙宇的远近位置，变化高低左右的相机位置，同时使用不同的焦段，用各种不同的视角记录了玉皇庙全景、中景、近景、特写等不同的景别，全面细致地记录下这次短暂的旅行。下面就紧跟着蚂蚁一起游览吧。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　玉皇庙建在公园中心位置的山坡上。建筑历史悠久，始建于元代，后经明清两代重修和扩建，才有了今天的规模，已有六百多年历史，主要供奉玉皇大帝的，每年正月初九，前来朝拜的人络绎不绝。毓璜顶又因其景色绝俗，恍如世外仙境，故又称为“小蓬菜”。整个玉皇庙建筑群仅仅千余平米，小巧雅致。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　平时的下午，这里只有散步的老人和公园的管理人员，所以拍照的时候，很少见到人。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一、玉皇庙外景○</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">来到玉皇庙前的广场（见下图1.1），仰望玉皇庙，因为台阶比较高，周围杂乱的设施不少，如果在这里拍摄玉皇庙的全景，几乎拍不到主体建筑的，显得主题不突出。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RG008-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">玉皇庙前广场/图1.1</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">蚂蚁绕过广场上的铁质焚香炉，拾级而上，狭小的入口处台阶处在阴影中，虽然能拍到玉皇庙，但效果仍然不理想（见下图1.2）。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RJ4a-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">玉皇庙前台阶/图1.2</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">台阶一直通到庙门前，想直接在正面拍下建筑，已经没有位置了。于是蚂蚁来到庙的左侧再向左拐弯处一块小的空地，从侧面可以拍到主体建筑的全景。但是，空地上的景物以及远处现代城市的建筑，或是遮挡或是干扰了要拍摄的庙宇。而且空地上的阴影过于明显，显得画面明显不协调（见右图1.3）。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">庙的左侧一块空地拍的玉皇庙全景</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RG342-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">树枝和现代建筑干扰到了玉皇庙 /图1.3</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">于是就尽量地向前走，躲过右侧的树木和大片的阴影。然后蹲下来低角度拍了下图1.4玉皇庙的全景。画面干净完整，建筑的气势也得到很好的表现。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">正面毕竟是要拍的，即便是前面没有位置，加上不想拍得规规矩矩没有新意，所以就在庙门前侧的台阶旁用更低的位置用广角继续拍了一张玉皇庙的中景照（见下图1.5）。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RID4-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>蹲下来低角度拍摄的玉皇庙，画面干净完整/图1.4</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RJ648-5.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>庙门的中景照 /图1.5</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">庙宇的两侧各有一个便门和高挑的角楼。蚂蚁竖着拍了一张角楼的全景照（见下图1.6）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">因为天气晴朗，角亭在湛蓝天空的衬托下显得更加金碧辉煌，所以用相机横着拍出大面积的天空，并用长焦拉近拍了张角楼的近景（见下图1.7）。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RI2a-6.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>角楼近景照 /图1.6</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RMb3-7.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>角亭近景照 /图1.7</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">拍完角亭，看见便门的造型小巧中蕴含庄重，于是蚂蚁规规矩矩地拍一张玉皇庙便门的全景（见下图1.8），便门上部的金字衬在蓝的底色上，非常精彩，凑近再拍张字的特写（见下图1.9）。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RJH5-8.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>便门的全景/图1.8</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RLY7-9.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>豁然开朗四个字的特写/图1.9</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">夕阳西下，金色的光线洒落在庙宇前，装饰的大大小小的灯笼显得很有生气。先抓住一只树上的小灯笼凑近了，拍一张特写（见下图1.10），然后在门廊下，从逆光的角度，用广角拍下落日光芒照亮的大灯笼，犹如就是从灯笼里发出光芒一样（见下图1.11）。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/2332091T3-0.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>灯笼的特写/图1.10</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/2332093115-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>逆光下的灯笼/图1.11</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">至此，蚂蚁使用多种景别将玉皇庙的外景（允许拍摄的部分）拍了一遍。然后进入玉皇庙，因为庙里拍摄的限制，也只能在很小的一部分范围内进行拍摄。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">二、玉皇庙内景○</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">蚂蚁逬入庙内，先来一张院子里的全景。当然是中规中矩的正面拍摄（见下图2.1），然后再从45度角拍一张（见下图2.2）。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/23320960W-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>正面拍摄的全景/图2.1</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/2332091911-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>45°角拍摄的全景/图2.2</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">蚂蚁再靠近拍了张正殿的中景照（见下图2.3），看到香炉里正在焚烧的供香，于是蚂蚁拍了张供香的特写（见下图2.4）。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RKV1-14.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>正殿的中景照/图2.3</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RJS0-15.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>供香的特写/图2.4</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接下来蚂蚁就无法再进一步地拍摄了。不要紧，正好是深入院子里拍摄细致景物的时候了。很多有意思的细节和局部，恰恰可以更好地记录下自己的感受，比如石头台阶、燃烧的香炉、炉子上的蜡烛液体的特写（见下图2.5-2.7）。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050391131-16.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>石头台阶/图2.5</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/10503a336-17.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>燃香的炉子/图2.6</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050392G7-18.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">炉子上的蜡烛液体的特写/图2.7</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/10503a027-19.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>门锁的特写/图2.8</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/10503aX5-20.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>房檐的特写/图2.9</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050395308-21.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>斑驳油漆的特写/图2.10</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050396403-22.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>窗户的特写/图2.11</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">到此为止，蚂蚁通过拍摄玉皇庙的外景和内景，并用不同的拍摄距离、不同的焦距和视角记录了玉皇庙的全景、中景、近景、特写等不同的景别，全面细致地记录下这次短暂的游览历程。现在小伙伴们应该知道把相机对着哪里拍了吧，都知道该如何选景了吧。再次旅行回来后，你发现你的照片，再也不是差不多的场景了，也记录下了让你印象深刻的景物，这时可别忘了感谢蚂蚁哦。</p><p><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050395038-23.jpg\"/></p>','2018-02-27 17:13:39','http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RI649-0.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RG008-1.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RJ4a-2.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RG342-3.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RID4-4.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RJ648-5.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RI2a-6.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RMb3-7.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RJH5-8.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RLY7-9.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/2332091T3-0.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/2332093115-1.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/23320960W-2.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/2332091911-3.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RKV1-14.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/232RJS0-15.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050391131-16.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/10503a336-17.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050392G7-18.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/10503a027-19.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/10503aX5-20.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050395308-21.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050396403-22.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050395038-23.jpg','摄影,风景','教你如何拍摄旅游摄影中的庙宇建筑',9,0,0,'Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用通俗易懂的语言5分钟教您拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教你如何拍摄旅游摄影中的庙宇建筑-玉皇庙。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，摄影艺术吧文字整理，如需转载请保留来源。　　春节期间，亲朋好友吃吃喝喝之后，难免会一起到比较有名的景点逛一逛，拍拍照，但很多小伙伴往往不知道该把相机对着哪里拍，也不清楚如何选景，拍什么不拍什么。旅',1,'http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/1050395038-23.jpg',NULL,4,0),(107,1,0,'<p style=\"text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用通俗易懂的语言5分钟教您拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教大家如何拍水滴。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，<a href=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;\">摄影艺术吧</a>文字整理，如需转载请保留来源</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942025034-0.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">内容简介：如何拍飞溅的水滴|示范机型：佳能700D</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">拍水滴可是个技术活儿，一般人拍不了，不信大家百度搜索一下，人家教程说了，要准备单反+微距镜头，要准备外置闪光灯并且要支持FP高速同步，据说还得用手动对焦，事实真的是这样吗？咱普通老百姓就拍不了？以前也许是，现在蚂蚁来了，一切都不一样了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">或许百度的水滴教程是教大脚怎么获得国际大奖的，但是咱普通老百姓谁又那个雄心壮志，我们只需拍出漂亮的水滴可以了，跟着蚂蚁的教程，你不需要几千元的单反，你不需要高级闪关灯和微距镜头，更不需要手动对焦，甚至就算你是个小菜鸟拿着1000出头的卡片机也出水滴，不信？跟着蚂蚁的教程赶紧开始吧。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942021318-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">感人并且震撼的水滴效果△图1</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">拍水滴的要领主要有以下四步：</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1/把相机安装在三脚架上，并且靠近水盆，尽量采用平视的拍摄角度；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2/调到TV档，设置1/100秒或则更快的快门速度，设置100-400的感亮度：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3/设置成连拍，开启闪光灯。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4/利用替代物来准确对焦。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">器材准备：</strong>三脚架，水盆等盛水器皿，滴水器材（可以用家里的水龙头，也可以找个塑料瓶在瓶盖上扎个洞把它架高，或者用滴管也可以，还可以用一次性杯子加牙签的牛逼组合）</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面赶紧进入我们的详细教程↓↓↓</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">第一/制作滴水装置</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你是一个人拍水滴，建议你用厨房或者卫生间的水龙头，但是这样可能背景不太好看。如果你是有人配合，可以用滴管，或者是以次性杯子下边扎一根牙签，让水顺着牙签滴下，又或者拿个矿泉水瓶子扎个洞都可以，这样的话就可以简单布置一下背景。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;text-decoration:underline;\">无论是什么样的滴水装置要掌握两个点：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1/水滴尽量匀速滴下，</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2/滴水位置最好固定不变，方便后期清楚抓拍。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当然除了滴水，你也可以滴饮料，滴牛奶，或者在水里滴水彩，这样你拍出来的东西就带色彩了，我们蚂蚁小伙伴拍过醒目饮料，淡淡的绿色很好看。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">盛水器皿就用塑料盆就可以了，尽量盛满水。水滴滴下的高度经过蚂蚁的反复试验在距水平面50厘米左右较合适，水滴溅起的高度大概在5厘米左右，太低了水滴溅起的不明显，影响效果，太高了水滴可能溅起落到器材上，不安全。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">第二/把相机架在三脚架上，并且靠近水盆，尽量采用平视的拍摄角度</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">把相机架在三脚架上，这样可以保证相机的稳定，更好的对焦，提高拍摄成功率。把相机尽量靠近水盆，并且可以适当的调节相机的变焦，使水滴更大程度的出现在相机视野中，这样能更好的表现水滴激起瞬间的细节（见图2）。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/094202N59-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最佳的滴水距离▽图2</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">建议大家尽量采用平视的拍摄角度，根据水滴溅起的高度调整相机的高度。平视的角度能更好的表现水花四溅的感觉，而且拍清楚的概率要远比俯拍大的多，不是很建议大家用俯拍的角度。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">第三/调到TV档，设置最低1/100秒快门速度，ISO设定为100-400</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">调到相机顶部上的转盘到TV档（即快门优先模式，有的相机也用S表示，见下图3.1），把快门速度调节为1/100S或者更快，把ISO设定为100-400之间就可以了（见下图3.2）。</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942022505-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图3.1</p><p><img class=\"img-responsive margin-top margin-bottom\" src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942024S8-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"/>图3.2</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">因为水滴落并溅起的瞬间非常短暂，经过蚂蚁的反复试验，想抓拍到这个细节最慢也要设置1/100S的快门，否则拍出的水滴模糊的概率很大。把感亮度ISO设定为100-</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">400之间均可，低ISO可以保证画质良好，不至于出来的照片噪点太多而影响画质。（<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;text-decoration:underline;\">什么是快门和ISO?快门速度和抓拍之间是什么关系？ISO和噪点之间又是什么关系？可以分别点击快门或ISO进入我们的教程</span>）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">你的相机没有TV或M模式，没法手动设置快门速度？好吧，这是个小小的悲剧，不过没关系，蚂蚁有办法，你就找个光线特别好的地方，采用P模式，ISO设置到400，此时相机自动设置的快门速度也可能会很快，也是可以抓拍到的。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">第四/设置成连拍模式</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">前面讲过了，水滴落下并溅起的瞬间实在是太短暂了，如果单张拍摄就要求我们必须精确预判水滴落下和溅起的时间点，快速对焦按快门才能抓拍的到，这可是个眼疾手快的活儿，对新手来说有点难度，怎么办？蚂蚁给你支招儿：<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;text-decoration:underline;\">经过蚂蚁的反复试验，设置连拍是最好的办法。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">尽量控制水滴以特定的频率持续滴下，我们在水滴溅起的瞬间按下快门不松开，相机会“咔咔咔”一直拍，持续5-10秒左右松开快门相机停止拍摄，然后我们在这些照片中筛比较好的就可以了，这要比靠预判和快速对焦按快门靠谱多了。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942021931-5.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">设置为连拍模式△图4</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第五/开启闪光灯</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">经过蚂蚁的反复试验发现，开启闪光灯摆设水滴能够更好的表现出水滴的质感，而且会把普通的水滴拍的晶莹剔透，效果你们懂的，而且开了闪光会让背景变得更黒，更好的突出水滴主体，所以强烈建议大家开启闪光灯。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有的相机设置连拍之后是无法开闪光的（比如索尼HX300就存在这个问题），或者开了闪光灯连拍速度会变慢，所以对这类相机就只能关闭闪光了。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/094202L63-6.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">闪光灯按钮△图5</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第六/利用替代物来对焦</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在准备工作和相机设置都妥妥的了，最重要的一步来了啊：准确对焦是关键。很多小伙伴问：<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;text-decoration:underline;\">那水滴溅起落下眨眼间的事儿，我怎么对焦？</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">蚂蚁有妙招儿：此时可以让你的小伙伴把一直钢笔或者筷子等替代物预先放在水滴滴落的位置（见图6），然后半按快门对焦在替代物上，并且注意对焦的高度差不多是水滴溅起的高度。对焦完成后，半按快门不松开，然后把替代物拿走，然后开始滴水，滴水时，眼睛不要盯着取景器，而是要盯着水滴，预判水滴溅起的瞬间全按快门一直连拍就可以了，哇哈哈哈。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942023608-7.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对焦高度与水滴溅起高度差不多△图6</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">好了，至此蚂蚁拍水滴的经验和技巧已经全部无私的分享完毕了，写的挺多，其实多实验几次你会发现其实掌握起来并不难，而且你会爱上拍水滴，因为拍出漂亮的水滴真的太有成就感了。接下来我们看一下蚂蚁团队拍摄的几组精彩水滴照片：</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/094202N61-8.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">飞溅的奶滴△图7，皇冠状水滴△图8，泛起涟漪的水滴 △图9</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942024912-9.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">晶莹剔透的水滴 △图10</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">最后再来总结下拍水滴的四个步骤：</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">1/把相机安装在三脚架上，并且靠近水盆，尽量采用平视的拍摄角度；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">2/调到TV档，设置1/100秒或则更快的快门速度，设置100-400的感亮度；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">3/设置成连拍，开启闪光灯</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\">4/利用替代功来准确对焦。</span></p><p><span style=\"color:#ff6600;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/094202J23-10.jpg\"/></p>','2018-02-27 17:15:39','http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942025034-0.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942021318-1.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/094202N59-2.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942022505-3.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942024S8-4.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942021931-5.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/094202L63-6.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942023608-7.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/094202N61-8.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/0942024912-9.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/094202J23-10.jpg','摄影,水滴','教你如何拍水滴',11,0,0,'Hello大家好！我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用通俗易懂的语言5分钟教您拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教大家如何拍水滴。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，摄影艺术吧文字整理，如需转载请保留来源内容简介：如何拍飞溅的水滴|示范机型：佳能700D拍水滴可是个技术活儿，一般人拍不了，不信大家百度搜索一下，人家教程说了，要准备单反+微距镜头，要准备外置闪光灯并且要支持FP高速同步',1,'http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1509/094202J23-10.jpg',NULL,4,0),(108,1,0,'<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/sheying/syjc/201508/783.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(180, 15, 42); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">如何拍创意集体照</strong></a></h3><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">导语Hello大家好!我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用最通俗易懂的语言5分钟教你拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教大家如何拍摄创意集体照。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，<a href=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;\">摄影艺术吧</a>文字整理，如需转载请保留来源。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/15294B496-0.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">内容简介：拍摄集体照的创意姿势 示范机型：佳能700D</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">难道我们每次拍集体照都要像个木头桩子似的站着任人摆布?难道我们每次拍集体照都要如此的千篇一律毫无新意？No!在蚂蚁的字典里，从来就没有循规蹈距，每个人心中都有无限的创造力，我们要敢于打破既定的规矩，今天蚂蚁团队小伙伴们集体出镜，给大家演示怎么拍出创意集体照，集体照姿势应该怎么摆才够有新意，才好玩，才能让人记得住！（本教程照片涉及到蚂蚁军团人物肖像权，如需转载请联系我们）</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529464Q4-1.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">千篇一律的木桩式集体照，对这样的集体张说NO！</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">01怎么让全身集体照不落俗套，那就是不要木头桩子似的傻站着，可以摆出不同的站姿和表情，叉腰，揣手，插屁兜，随便你了，只要别保持立正姿势就好了，这样不至于让画面显得呆板和俗套。见下图1.1中左一和右一两个生表现的就很不错，一个是模特走完T台摆POSE，一个是＂我是大姐我怕谁＂的范儿，拍完的效果有没有越狱海报的感觉？小小的改变马上就出效果了吧。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/15294BF8-2.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">全身集体照尽量摆出不同的姿势图1.1</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529463N1-3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《越狱》海报图1.2</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">02全身集体照还可以摆出右图这种POSE，非常适合一个小团体拍摄集体照，让团队的领军人物站在中间并且靠前一些，随便摆出一个霸气侧漏的姿势，后面的团队成员分成三排在两侧站立，立体感较强而且整体造型也会有不落俗套的效果。下图右2那哥们演的太入戏了，有点抢老大的风头了，下次注意哦，否则很容易被封杀啊。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529464558-4.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">全身集体照尽量摆出不同的姿势图2</strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">03在拍集体照时，很多时候可以采用半身照的形式。如果人数较多，还是采用多排站立的方式比较好，这样不至于出现一排依次站开的古板姿势，多排站立可以让集体照有层次感，拍的时候把大家当成一个整体来拍，保证每个人都有露面，不能被遮挡。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/15294A616-5.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">多拍站立的半身集体照图3</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">04多排站立也应该尽量摆出有创意的姿势，随时和古板，俗套做斗争，如下图4，选择一个笑容最好看的小伙伴在最前方展现出超灿烂的笑容，后面的小伙伴一个跟着一个靠着前面那个站着来拍照，注意最前面的那个一定要笑的尽量灿烂，因为这种情绪是可以向后传递的，见下图4最后面那姐们儿，已经完全笑崩了，频临失控的边缘。</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529464000-6.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">尽量摆出有创意的姿势图4</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">05下图5这种姿势有点像前一种的演变版，同样是分多排站立，同样选择一个最靠前的在中间，其余的小伙伴在后面分别探出头来，注意大家一起看向镜头，嗨，左一那哥们儿看哪呢？看啥看，就说你呢！</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529461051-7.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">多排站立一次散开图5</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">06如果上面这些半身集体照都不能满足你，有时候还可以尝试变换拍摄角度，爬上露台或者台阶等较高的地方往下拍，这会让照片变得更加有吸引力和有趣，而且这个拍法还有个好处就是会让人不自觉的把眼睛挣大，显得非常有神，见下图6中小伙伴们眼睛都很大，有木有？有木有？</p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529464632-8.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, simsun, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;box-sizing: border-box;\">尝试采用俯拍的角度图6</span></strong></p><p><br/></p>','2018-02-27 17:17:27','http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/15294B496-0.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529464Q4-1.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/15294BF8-2.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529463N1-3.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529464558-4.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/15294A616-5.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529464000-6.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529461051-7.jpg,http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529464632-8.jpg','摄影,集体照','如何拍创意集体照',4,0,0,'如何拍创意集体照导语Hello大家好!我们是蚂蚁摄影，您身边懂摄影的好朋友。不要枯燥，不要复杂，不要理论，我们会用最通俗易懂的语言5分钟教你拍出好照片。今天蚂蚁摄影教大家如何拍摄创意集体照。本教程蚂蚁摄影原创，摄影艺术吧文字整理，如需转载请保留来源。内容简介：拍摄集体照的创意姿势 示范机型：佳能700D难道我们每次拍集体照都要像个木头桩子似的站着任人摆布?难道我们每次拍集体照都要如此的千篇一律毫无',4,'http://www.chinaart8.com/uploads/allimg/1508/1529464632-8.jpg',NULL,4,0),(109,1,0,'<p>《花谢花飞花满天》是由北京东方飞云国际影视股份有限公司出品，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%B5%96%E6%B0%B4%E6%B8%85\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">赖水清</a>执导，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BD%95%E6%B6%A6%E4%B8%9C\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">何润东</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%BC%A0%E9%A6%A8%E4%BA%88/26128\" data-lemmaid=\"26128\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">张馨予</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%9C%B1%E4%B8%80%E9%BE%99\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">朱一龙</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%9D%8E%E5%BF%83%E8%89%BE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">李心艾</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%9C%B1%E6%A2%93%E9%AA%81\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">朱梓骁</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%BD%A4\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">于小彤</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%8E%E9%9D%92%E6%96%8C\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">于青斌</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%9D%A8%E5%87%80%E5%A6%82\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">杨净如</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%AB%98%E6%9B%99%E5%85%89\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">高曙光</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%8E%8B%E8%89%B3/16486\" data-lemmaid=\"16486\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">王艳</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%AA%9A\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">周海媚</a>等人主演的古装悬疑情感大剧<span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: pointer; padding: 0px 2px;\">[1]</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;。</p><p>该剧讲述了倾城不慎受伤失忆，花满天历经万难之后找到了“千寻”，并救其于水深火热之中，两人萌生情愫的故事<span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: pointer; padding: 0px 2px;\">[2]</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;。</p><p>该剧于2017年12月4日在浙江卫视首播<span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: pointer; padding: 0px 2px;\">[3]</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;。</p><p><br/></p>','2018-02-27 17:24:26','/upload/cover/1/qqqqqqqqqq8.jpg','影视','花谢花飞花满天',7,0,0,'《花谢花飞花满天》是由北京东方飞云国际影视股份有限公司出品，赖水清执导，何润东、张馨予、朱一龙、李心艾、朱梓骁、于小彤、于青斌、杨净如、高曙光、王艳、周海媚等人主演的古装悬疑情感大剧[1]&nbsp;&nbsp;。该剧讲述了倾城不慎受伤失忆，花满天历经万难之后找到了“千寻”，并救其于水深火热之中，两人萌生情愫的故事[2]&nbsp;&nbsp;。该剧于2017年12月4日在浙江卫视首播[3]&nb',2,'/upload/cover/1/qqqqqqqqqq8.jpg','https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=jb6wejrvi609u6f&tiny=0&auto=0',3,NULL),(110,1,0,'<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">Java开发概述：</span></h2><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使用Java做Web应用开发已经有近20年的历史了，从最初的Servlet1.0一步步演化到现在如此多的框架，库以及整个生态系统。经过这么长时间的发展，Java作为一个成熟的语言，也演化出了非常成熟的生态系统，这也是许多公司采用Java作为主流的语言进行服务器端开发的原因，也是为什么Java一直保持着非常活跃的用户群。然而这个生态系统纷繁复杂，一个非常简单的Java Web应用程序都有可能应用到以下技术：</span><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-bb9f2b9a205a4d3eb0c3acab830b7c46_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1268\" data-rawheight=\"672\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1268\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb9f2b9a205a4d3eb0c3acab830b7c46_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb9f2b9a205a4d3eb0c3acab830b7c46_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Java开发分为两个阵营，一个是由Oracle 为代表的Java EE阵营，这是Web开发的官方参考标准。其中核心技术主要有Servlet, EJB, JMS, JSF, JDBC/JPA, JAXB, JAX-WS等。另一个阵营则是由开源社区以及Pivotal代表的Spring阵营，其中核心技术主要有 Spring Framework, Spring MVC, Spring Data, Spring Security等等。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Spring从最开始作为依赖注入的Bean container，逐渐发展为Java应用开发的主流框架。Java EE因为其臃肿，复杂，难以使用的结构，被很多Java程序员抛弃。从Java EE6开始才引入了CDI (Context Dependency Injection)，而且Java EE 的设计思想非常学术化, Gavin King等人脱离了工业界的需求，使得Java EE开发非常复杂。JSF甚至为Java之父James Gosling诟病。相反在Spring社区，越来越多现代化的应用开发方法被融入进来，形成不同的Spring项目。</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">什么是Spring Boot?</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Spring Boot便是一个社区反馈推动的项目. Spring Boot可以说是至少近5年来Spring乃至整个Java社区最有影响力的项目之一。Spring Boot主要包含以下特性：<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"/></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">直接嵌入Tomcat, Jetty或者Undertow作为Servlet container。从此之后再也不用将应用程序打包成war然后上传到application server里面了。</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">提供了starter POM, 能够非常方便的进行包管理, 很大程度上减少了jar hell或者dependency hell</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">自动进行Spring框架的配置，节省程序员大量的时间和精力，能够让程序员专注在业务逻辑代码的编写上</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">不需要任何第三方系统, Spring Boot自带了可以用于生产环境的程序状态信息和健康状态。同时可以让应用程序非常方便的读取外部的配置信息</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">完全不需要任何代码的自动生成。更不需要用xml来进行框架的配置</p></li></ul><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">为什么Spring Boot是颠覆性的？</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为什么说Spring Boot是颠覆性的呢？因为它彻底改变了Java应用开发的模式。以往我们做Spring应用开发，要知道配置哪些类来让Hibernate和Spring一起工作，要知道如何配置view resolver来控制哪个模版进行视图层的展示。经常写了一大堆代码之后发现只是在处理Spring框架本身的配置，根本一行业务逻辑都没有写。开发完成之后，我们还要考虑部署的问题，且不说部署到非常笨重的应用服务器，比如WebSphere, Weblogic或者JBoss，即使部署到Tomcat或者Jetty这种轻量级容器上面，我们要知道如何配置容器，如何修改配置文件等等。而且在多应用部署到同一个Tomcat的时候，经常会出现冲突。就算我们花了很大力气解决了这些问题，程序部署成功之后，我们很难去了解这个程序的运行状态。有可能我们要配置很多第三方工具来去知道这个应用程序运行状态如何，有哪些参数，环境变量是什么。尽管Spring帮我们解决了依赖注入的问题，简化了一些MVC的流程，但是Spring框架本身集成了越来越多东西，导致其越来越难配置，维护成本成直线上升。很多时候Java程序员们看到Python, Ruby或者JavaScript程序员敲几个命令安装一些库，然后简单的敲几行代码，引入一些框架比如flask，然后直接一个简单的API就可以跑起来了。这时候Java程序员可能还在研究该使用Maven里面的哪个库，如何在代码里面进行配置呢。大家心里的表情肯定是这样：</p><p><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-dea3429dec7d46af171356781354def8_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"922\" data-rawheight=\"910\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"922\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-dea3429dec7d46af171356781354def8_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-dea3429dec7d46af171356781354def8_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(求此时Java程序员心理阴影面积)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Java程序员扬眉吐气的时候到了！</p><p><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-23d19c2d6754173788093180e756c55b_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"504\" data-rawheight=\"424\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"504\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-23d19c2d6754173788093180e756c55b_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-23d19c2d6754173788093180e756c55b_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 20px 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">传统Spring开发对决Spring Boot应用开发</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接下来我会通过具体例子对比传统的Spring应用开发和Spring Boot应用开发。假如我们开发一个Hello World的REST API，传统的Spring开发应该这么做.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. 如果使用Maven进行包管理，编写pom.xml 如下</p><p><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-0c1b58b96f70ba05bfeecfb95f6f8796_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"914\" data-rawheight=\"904\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"914\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0c1b58b96f70ba05bfeecfb95f6f8796_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0c1b58b96f70ba05bfeecfb95f6f8796_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-7dd23f22211de11fc95109133ba0ede4_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"936\" data-rawheight=\"690\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"936\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7dd23f22211de11fc95109133ba0ede4_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7dd23f22211de11fc95109133ba0ede4_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如上可以看到为了编写简单的hello world REST API我们引入了Spring Core, Spring Web, Spring Web MVC, Java Servlet and Jackson这么多包依赖。可以想象复杂一点的程序这个pom会变成什么样。。。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 编写HelloWorldInitializer class如下<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"/></p><p><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-33c638a4beb2b4c2079affae941e4ff5_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1026\" data-rawheight=\"314\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1026\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-33c638a4beb2b4c2079affae941e4ff5_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-33c638a4beb2b4c2079affae941e4ff5_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这个已经是非常简单的Java Config了，在Servlet 3.0之前用XML配置Spring的小伙伴们现在估计已经崩溃。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 编写HelloWorldConfiguration class<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"/></p><p><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-53fc57cd7b6c2714841ac8cf9ce7b94a_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"906\" data-rawheight=\"336\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"906\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-53fc57cd7b6c2714841ac8cf9ce7b94a_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-53fc57cd7b6c2714841ac8cf9ce7b94a_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注意到我们这个类里面一行业务逻辑都没有哦。。。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;