pg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2d1da5df5e2d6b50e18bcd1f795a2c5e_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-795fbb0b90540b9849dce82b0d0cd7b8_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"904\" data-rawheight=\"522\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"904\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-795fbb0b90540b9849dce82b0d0cd7b8_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-795fbb0b90540b9849dce82b0d0cd7b8_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注意到我们只引入了一个包依赖，并且版本什么的就随他去吧</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 编写main 函数<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"/></