0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 编写HelloWorldRestController</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7941830c65c09c0ea53490895d5aede5_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"906\" data-rawheight=\"364\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"906\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7941830c65c09c0ea53490895d5aede5_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7941830c65c09c0ea53490895d5aede5_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4. 直接启动应用程序，不需要部署</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-53ca2d14ca0c252989e6219aae4ba04a_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1038\" data-rawheight=\"198\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1038\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-53ca2d14ca0c252989e6219aae4ba04a_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-53ca2d14ca0c252989e6219aae4ba04a_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; cursor: zoom-in;\"/></figure><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5. 访问</span><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//localhost%3A8080\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" data-za-detail-view-id=\"1043\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 85, 153); text-decoration-line: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(68, 68, 68, 0.72); word-break: break-all; cursor: pointer; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"invisible\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; font-family: a; color: transparent; text-shadow: none; background-color: transparent;\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">localhost:8080</span><span class=\"invisible\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; font-family: a; color: transparent; text-shadow: none; background-color: transparent;\"></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;就可以直接看到Hello World了</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><figure style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 24px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a410c97966ad66a7364ecbf04cf07b47_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"396\" data-rawheight=\"132\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"396\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a410c97966ad66a7364ecbf04cf07b47_b.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; overflow: hidden; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"/></figure></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">之前HelloWorld程序对于新手来说至少要花个10-20分钟之类的，有了SpringBoot, 最多3分钟之内搞定HelloWorld不是梦。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 600;\">总结</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这里我只是简单的对SpringBoot进行了讲解，SpringBoot有非常多值得深入讨论的东西，它不仅让我们做Java开发变的简单有效，更重要的是SpringBoot彻底颠覆了我们对Java开发的认识，让我们第一次有了”原来Java开发可以这么做” 的感觉。有了SpringBoot之后，Java程序员可以更专注于业务逻辑，进行更敏捷的开发。</p><p><br/></p>','2018-03-06 15:09:04','https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-bb9f2b9a205a4d3eb0c3acab830b7c46_hd.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb9f2b9a205a4d3eb0c3acab830b7c46_b.jpg,https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-dea3429dec7d46af171356781354def8_hd.jpg,https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-dea3429dec7d46af171356781354def8_b.jpg,https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-23d19c2d6754173788093180e756c55b_hd.jpg,https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-23d19c2d6754173788093180e756c55b_b.jpg,https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-0c1b58b96f70ba05bfeecfb95f6f8796_hd.jpg,https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0c1b58b96f70ba05bfeecfb95f6f8796_b.jpg,https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-7dd23f22211de11fc95109133ba0ede4_hd.jpg,https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7dd23f22211de11fc95109133ba0ede4_b.jpg,https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-33c638a4beb2b4c2079affae941e4ff5_hd.jpg,https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-33c638a4beb2b4c2079affae941e4ff5_b.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-53fc57cd7b6c2714841ac8cf9ce7b94a_hd.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-53fc57cd7b6c2714841ac8cf9ce7b94a_b.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d47e9c00d62f5c632e7f78d987457cdf_hd.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d47e9c00d62f5c632e7f78d987457cdf_b.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-376c09c407828ffbf58cb1a820e73810_hd.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-376c09c407828ffbf58cb1a820e73810_b.jpg,https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-2d1da5df5e2d6b50e18bcd1f795a2c5e_hd.jpg,https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2d1da5df5e2d6b50e18bcd1f795a2c5e_b.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-795fbb0b90540b9849dce82b0d0cd7b8_hd.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-795fbb0b90540b9849dce82b0d0cd7b8_b.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-55d4194afea30b8d164ec2fe9b862abf_hd.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-55d4194afea30b8d164ec2fe9b862abf_b.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7941830c65c09c0ea53490895d5aede5_hd.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7941830c65c09c0ea53490895d5aede5_b.jpg,https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-53ca2d14ca0c252989e6219aae4ba04a_hd.jpg,https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-53ca2d14ca0c252989e6219aae4ba04a_b.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a410c97966ad66a7364ecbf04cf07b47_hd.jpg,https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a410c97966ad66a7364ecbf04cf07b47_b.jpg','Spring Boot,Java','用Spring Boot颠覆Java应用开发',21,0,0,'Java开发概述：使用Java做Web应用开发已经有近20年的历史了，从最初的Servlet1.0一步步演化到现在如此多的框架，库以及整个生态系统。经过这么长时间的发展，Java作为一个成熟的语言，也演化出了非常成熟的生态系统，这也是许多公司采用Java作为主流的语言进行服务器端开发的原因，也是为什么Java一直保持着非常活跃的用户群。然而这个生态系统纷繁复杂，一个非常简单的Java Web应用程',1,'https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a410c97966ad66a7364ecbf04cf07b47_b.jpg',NULL,1,0),(111,7,0,'<h1 id=\"前言\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.6rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);\">前言</h1><p style=\"margin: 0.85em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);\">前面几章我们见识了SpringBoot为我们做的自动配置，确实方便快捷，但是对于新手来说，如果不大懂SpringBoot内部启动原理，以后难免会吃亏。所以这次博主就跟你们一起一步步揭开SpringBoot的神秘面纱，让它不在神秘。</p><h1 id=\"正文\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.6rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);\"><a href=\"http://tengj.top/2017/03/09/springboot3/#%E6%AD%A3%E6%96%87\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"正文\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 25.6px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(37, 143, 184);\"></a>正文</h1><p style=\"margin: 0.85em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);\">我们开发任何一个Spring Boot项目，都会用到如下的启动类<br/></p><p><figure class=\"highlight java\" style=\"background: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.85); margin: 0.5em auto 1em; padding: 0.35em 1.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-width: 1px; overflow: auto; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); line-height: 1.3rem; border-radius: 2px; max-height: 50em; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 1px 1px 1px; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><table width=\"NaN\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 35px;\" class=\"firstRow\"><td class=\"gutter\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: middle; white-space: nowrap;\" height=\"35\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em 0px 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Inconsolata, Monaco, monospace, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;; font-size: 0.85rem; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: none; background-color: initial; overflow: auto; color: rgb(211, 211, 211); line-height: 1.3rem; text-align: right;\"><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">1</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">2</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">3</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">4</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">5</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">6</span><br/></pre></td><td class=\"code\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: middle;\" height=\"35\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Inconsolata, Monaco, monospace, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: none; background-color: initial; overflow: auto; line-height: 1.3rem;\"><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">@SpringBootApplication</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\"><span class=\"keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(204, 153, 204);\">public</span> <span class=\"class\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 204, 153);\"><span class=\"keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(204, 153, 204);\">class</span> <span class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">Application</span> </span>{</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"function\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 153, 204);\"><span class=\"keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(204, 153, 204);\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(204, 153, 204);\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(204, 153, 204);\">void</span> <span class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">main</span><span class=\"params\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(249, 145, 87);\">(String[] args)</span> </span>{</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;SpringApplication.run(Application.class, args);</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;}</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">}</span><br/></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></p><p style=\"margin: 0.85em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0.85em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);\">从上面代码可以看出，Annotation定义（@SpringBootApplication）和类定义（SpringApplication.run）最为耀眼，所以要揭开SpringBoot的神秘面纱，我们要从这两位开始就可以了。</p><h2 id=\"SpringBootApplication背后的秘密\" style=\"margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-family: Times, Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 190, 102); text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);\"><a href=\"http://tengj.top/2017/03/09/springboot3/#SpringBootApplication%E8%83%8C%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SpringBootApplication背后的秘密\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(37, 143, 184);\"></a>SpringBootApplication背后的秘密</h2><p><figure class=\"highlight java\" style=\"background: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.85); margin: 0.5em auto 1em; padding: 0.35em 1.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-width: 1px; overflow: auto; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); line-height: 1.3rem; border-radius: 2px; max-height: 50em; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 1px 1px 1px; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-spa