beans-3.0.xsd&quot;</span></span></span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\"><span class=\"tag\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(242, 119, 122);\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"attr\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">default-lazy-init</span>=<span class=\"string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 204, 153);\">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"comment\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">&lt;!--bean定义--&gt;</span></span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\"><span class=\"tag\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(242, 119, 122);\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">beans</span>&gt;</span></span><br/></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 0.85em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);\">而基于JavaConfig的配置方式是这样：<br/></p><p><figure class=\"highlight java\" style=\"background: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.85); margin: 0.5em auto 1em; padding: 0.35em 1.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-width: 1px; overflow: auto; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); line-height: 1.3rem; border-radius: 2px; max-height: 50em; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 1px 1px 1px; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><table width=\"NaN\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; height: 35px;\" class=\"firstRow\"><td class=\"gutter\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: middle; white-space: nowrap;\" height=\"35\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em 0px 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Inconsolata, Monaco, monospace, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;; font-size: 0.85rem; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: none; background-color: initial; overflow: auto; color: rgb(211, 211, 211); line-height: 1.3rem; text-align: right;\"><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">1</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">2</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">3</span><br/><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.6px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3rem;\">4</span><br/></pre></td><td class=\"code\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: middle;\" height=\"35\"><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Inconsolata, Monaco, monospace, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: none; background-color: initial; overflow: auto; line-height: 1.3rem;\"><span class=\"line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; verti